  "text": "Plasma total cholesterol levels after 7 months on the diet were approximately 346 + 60 mg/100 ml as compared with 119 6 mg/100 ml in male C57BL/6J mice fed the control diet. These values are in agreement with our previous observation [CITATION_1] , and no significant elevation in either plasma-free fatty acids or triglyceride levels was observed.",
